@startuml invoice_to_cash

title Finance L2 - Invoice-to-Cash (ServiceCo)

start

:Receive service usage / time reports\nfrom Service Delivery;
:Validate completeness & exceptions;
if (Data valid?) then (yes)
  :Generate invoice draft;
  :Apply pricing rules & taxes;
  :Finance review & approval;
  :Issue invoice to client;
  :Record AR entry in accounting;
  :Monitor due date & reminders;
  if (Payment received?) then (yes)
    :Match payment to invoice;
    :Reconcile differences (if any);
    :Update AR aging & KPIs;
  else (no)
    :Escalate to collections / account manager;
  endif
else (no)
  :Return to Service Delivery\nfor correction;
endif

stop

@enduml
